"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/icon-04.png","title":"Free Shipping, Fast Arrival"}},"bottom_policy_r4ePHN":{"type":"bottom_policy","settings":{"add_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/contact-us","icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/icon-04.png","title":"24\/7 Support →"}},"collapsible_text_pUtNTG":{"type":"collapsible_text","disabled":true,"settings":{"enable_group":true,"font_transform":"capitalize","background_group":"","icon":"none","icon_width":20,"title":"Product Details","content":"<ul><li>Dynamic Lumbar Support for All-Day Comfort: AutoFull G7 office chair features a 1.18-inch dual-mode lumbar support that automatically adjusts to different sitting postures, providing precise and comfortable back support whether you're leaning forward, sitting upright, or reclining, effectively relieving lower back pain from long-term use.<\/li><li>4D Ergonomic Neck Pillow: Unlike regular headrests, AutoFull G7 desk chair offers forward and backward adjustment with a larger dual-axis rotation range, adapting to various gaming, working, or studying postures, providing comfortable neck support and relieving neck pain from prolonged use, catering to different body types and movements.<\/li><li>720° Dual-Axis Rotating Armrests: The armrests on this computer chair offer full 720° rotation and multi-dimensional adjustments, including 2.76-inch height adjustment, 2.36-inch front-back sliding, and 360° rotation for both the armrest surface and handle, ensuring stable arm support for different scenarios, preventing arm pain during long sessions.<\/li><li>140° Zero-Gravity Recline: With 4-position free-stop adjustment, our desk chair meets the reclining needs for office work, watching videos, and taking breaks. The Auto-balance induction chassis allows smooth reclining for light users and easy standing up for heavy users, perfect for relaxing activities.<\/li><li>Precise Fit for Various Body Types: All components of the AutoFull office chair are height-adjustable, precisely fitting users from 5.1ft to 6.5ft. Adjustments include 1.57-inch lumbar support, 2.56-inch backrest, 1.77-inch headrest, 3.15-inch seat height, 2.76-inch armrest, and 1.97-inch sliding seat cushion, ensuring everyone finds their ideal sitting position.<\/li><li>Stylish DesStylish Design & RGB Lighting: The unique RGB lighting module on the office chair creates a cool gaming atmosphere. The removable laser-back panel allows for quick customization without screws, letting you design your chair's appearance and create a personalized space.ign & RGB Lighting: The unique RGB lighting module on the office chair creates a cool gaming atmosphere. The removable laser-back panel allows for quick customization without screws, letting you design your chair's appearance and create a personalized space.<\/li><li>Durability & Safety: In line with BIFMA international standards, the AutoFull gaming chair meets top - level quality and safety requirements. It uses a Level 4 cylinder with SGS\/TUV dual accreditation for maximum safety. Plus, its PU - wrapped quiet wheels protect floors and move silently.<\/li><li>After-sales Service: AutoFull gaming chair provides users with 36 months of parts replacement or repair service. If you have any suggestions for our computer chair, please feel free to contact us.<\/li><\/ul>","page":""}},"collapsible_text_qEYXRB":{"type":"collapsible_text","disabled":true,"settings":{"enable_group":true,"font_transform":"capitalize","background_group":"","icon":"none","icon_width":20,"title":"WHAT'S INCLUDED","content":"<p>Share some content to your customers about your products.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_text_Dn9Bhc":{"type":"collapsible_text","disabled":true,"settings":{"enable_group":true,"font_transform":"capitalize","background_group":"","icon":"none","icon_width":20,"title":"Shipping Policy","content":"<p>Free Shipping – No minimum purchase required (available regions only).<\/p><p>Available Region: United States<\/p><p>Restricted shipping destinations include Puerto Rico (PR), Hawaii (HI), Guam (GU), and Alaska (AK).<\/p><p>Processing: 1-2 business days<\/p><p>Delivery: 3-7 business days via FedEx\/UPS<\/p><p>Tracking: Email sent with tracking number upon shipment<\/p><p>* Exceptions may apply to distant and\/or less accessible locations. We do not ship to PO boxes and Military APO, FPO and DPO destinations. <\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_text_wzAPgV":{"type":"collapsible_text","disabled":true,"settings":{"enable_group":true,"font_transform":"capitalize","background_group":"","icon":"none","icon_width":20,"title":"Return Policy","content":"<p>Returns Accepted Within 14 Days<\/p><p>✔ Unused, original condition & packaging<\/p><p>✔ Proof of purchase required<\/p><p>✖ Custom\/personalized items excluded<\/p><p><\/p><p>How to Return<\/p><p>Email <a href=\"mailto:service@autofull.com\" target=\"_blank\">service@autofull.com<\/a> for return instructions<\/p><p>Ship to:1521 E Francis St, Ontario, CA 91761Attn: WYD-HZAF66-EC<\/p><p>Shipping Costs<\/p><p>• Customer pays for change-of-mind returns<\/p><p>• We cover defective\/wrong item returns<\/p><p>Refund Process<\/p><p>• No restocking fees<\/p><p>• Refund to original payment method (3-5 business days after inspection)<\/p><p>Need Help?Contact us if refund doesn't appear after checking with your bank.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_text_7Dd44R":{"type":"collapsible_text","disabled":true,"settings":{"enable_group":true,"font_transform":"capitalize","background_group":"","icon":"none","icon_width":20,"title":"Warranty","content":"<p>AutoFull provides full product responsibility for 3 years from the date of purchase for most items.<\/p>","page":""}},"custom_logos_Fn4hg4":{"type":"custom_logos","disabled":true,"settings":{"allow_inline":true,"allow_flex":"space-around","allow_gap":20,"image1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IGR.png","alignment1":"start","max_width1":150,"image2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/SGS.png","alignment2":"start","max_width2":150,"image3":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/BIFMA.png","align